snippet.title: World of Kings Gameplay
snippet.description:
Official Launch on 30. May! World of Kings is a 3D fantasy MMORPG with massive map and various contents.

Right now you could pre-register on our official site for great in-game rewards!

Official Site: https://www.zloong.com/wwhd/?s=Y01
iOS link: https://apple.co/2PbqRIF
Google Play link: https://bit.ly/2Ug4wKZ

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WorldofKingsEN/
Discord: https://discord.gg/KpAsHGT
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/WorldofKings/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WorldofKings2
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/world_of_kings2019/
